Rising stars in the digital cosmos: companies showing significant growth in the technology sector;
Sailing under the 'Technology' banner: companies categorized under the Technology sector;
Vast ocean of the 'S&P 500': part of the S&P 500 index, which is a major stock market index;
Lightening their sails by more than 2.5%: stocks that show a percentage increase greater than 2.5% in the next day's closing price.

sql:
SELECT sector_id
FROM sectors
WHERE market_cap = (
    SELECT MAX(market_cap)
    FROM sectors
);

SELECT cdate, cp
FROM market_data
WHERE volume > 1000000 AND source_id = 1;
